# Config: menus

&rarr; [Templates: default menus](help_templates_menus)

---
## Base

To configure a menu in a plugin's part, define it as follow:

<pre class="syntax yaml">
<em>PluginName:</em>
  <em>menus:</em>
    <em>menuName:</em>
      [menu configuration]
</pre>

You can base your configuration on the [default configuration for a menu](help_config_defaults#menu)